Speaker 1: So that's a lot, so that's not the same, so let me give you some info, so yes, it is Indenafil and it is Viagra, and you would not get the same thing online for $5, that'd be cheap stuff from India and China.

Speaker 2: Well, I don't know if it's not cheap stuff either, this is generic, in Viagra, FDA approved.

Speaker 1: FDA approved, no it's not, that's not true, that's not true at all, that's why people even shop with us, because when you look it up, we're the ones that sell FDA approved Viagra, and that's why it doesn't cost $5, because it's real Viagra, and not the cheap stuff that's actually gonna hurt you, and you don't know what country it's coming from with no federally approved regulatory systems to check their medications, that's why they sell it for so cheap, it's coming out of some little warehouse in India.

Speaker 2: No, I want what you guys said, you guys did not say in the ad that I'm getting generic Viagra.
